### 글 작성
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/posts
#Authorization:{{Authorization}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "{{title}}",
  "content": "{{content}}",
  "theme" : "{{theme}}",
  "address" : "{{address}}",
  "placeName" : "{{place-name}}"
}



### 글 삭제
DELETE localhost:8080/v1/posts/{{post-id}}


### 글 조회
GET localhost:8080/v1/posts/place-name
    ?page=1&theme={{theme}}&short-address={{short-address}}


### 글 아이디 제목 조회
GET localhost:8080/v1/posts
    ?place-name={{place-name}}&page=1&q={{q}}&sort-by={{sort-by}}


### 글 수정
PATCH localhost:8080/v1/posts/{{post-id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "{{edit_title}}",
  "content": "{{edit_content}}"
}



### 글 단권 조회
GET localhost:8080/v1/posts/{{post-id}}
